{"tid":1040104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高層靠估兩年後打柴？華為承認 Mate X 未有測試數據","createTime":"2019-02-28T00:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T01:49:17.000Z","uid":10717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a1e524a04fe5eb0ef9b7a317f063a75f023f02","tid":1040104,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:33:24.000Z","msg":"華為日前公佈旗下首款摺疊屏幕手機 Mate X，這不但是市場首批上市的新款摺機，亦是首批公佈支援 5G 網絡的手機，不過高達 2,299 歐元（折合 HK$20,496）的定價令人卻步。雖然很多手機愛好者不介意出重金去體驗這款 5G 摺機，但還是希望能夠耐用一點。<br />\n<br />\n高層靠估兩年後打柴？華為承認 Mate X 未有測試數據<br />\n<br />\n究竟這個被大陸傳媒稱為「鷹翼」式摺疊設計有幾耐用呢？華為消費業務手機產品線總裁何剛接受大陸傳媒訪問時直言，「具體次數現在還不能說，因為沒有正式上市，華為還要做更多實驗，但是不管怎麼說，我們一定要達到消費者使用以後，至少我覺得不用太長，至少兩年時間不要出現任何問題，滿足消費者日常使用體驗，這是華為的要求。」<br />\n<br />\n高層靠估兩年後打柴？華為承認 Mate X 未有測試數據<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，即是華為本身沒有屏幕和鉸位等可摺疊次數的數據，而且雖然正式發表了，但實驗測試似乎尚未完成。另外，華為高層並非以客觀而科學化，例如一般消費者每天使用手機的次數作為基準去回覆，反而是他個人覺得「不用太長，至少兩年不出現問題」。<span style=\"color: red;\">華為曾表示 Mate X 花了工程師 3 年時間開發，網友相信會不掌握可摺疊次數的數據嗎？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pfxaS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pfxaS2.png&h=a6cb4715&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5ncaS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5ncaS2.png&h=6122cec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73m8tEX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73m8tEX.png&h=95bb9f35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09wTEMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09wTEMC.png&h=6bf034d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fx14MrD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFx14MrD.png&h=7e5646c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n供應商公版方案話3年研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3651e2485df8edc390f600841de0d67ed0f0b26","tid":1040104,"uid":121146,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"偷返黎 唔知好正常姐"},{"pid":"454cdc4f250a51d19765ab61cfce63a7213cba44","tid":1040104,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3651e2485df8edc390f600841de0d67ed0f0b26","tid":1040104,"uid":121146,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"偷返黎 唔知好正常姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"砌機一部  都未摸熟摺芒技術"},{"pid":"31bc8622787f8239b1f499fbbcafd1a6e4390896","tid":1040104,"uid":57787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:18:03.000Z","msg":"即係概念機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98edc18540ba99e4fabcc7aa1bbc775ecb031d6","tid":1040104,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:22:47.000Z","msg":"是撚但但<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9f69a6703829d515c093a51a1df4e52e90410b","tid":1040104,"uid":68620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"偷返黎姐"},{"pid":"d77c9a9108fc7620a142cd4c8c93a9b174e446fa","tid":1040104,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3651e2485df8edc390f600841de0d67ed0f0b26","tid":1040104,"uid":121146,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"偷返黎 唔知好正常姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"買技術返來，宣布話自主研發<br />\n<br />\n個原創者有出來嘈，話佢無恥"},{"pid":"79431dcc3f6f9fb0ef7599390db1b1abb2308b42","tid":1040104,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3651e2485df8edc390f600841de0d67ed0f0b26","tid":1040104,"uid":121146,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"偷返黎 唔知好正常姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:26:55.000Z","msg